    RoutineAdapterFactory

    public static class RoutineAdapterFactory.Builder
extends Object
implements com.github.dm.jrt.core.config.InvocationConfigurable<RoutineAdapterFactory.Builder>
    Builder of routine adapter factory instances.

    The options set through the builder configuration will be applied to all the routine handling the Retrofit calls, unless they are overwritten by specific annotations.

    See Also:
    ReflectionRoutineBuilders.getInvocationMode(Method), ReflectionRoutineBuilders.withAnnotations(InvocationConfiguration, Annotation...)
